name: Experiment Or Die #140
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. I've always been  interested and attracted to signage and not just vintage neon type signs but also every day informational stuff that you can find on just about any city wall. The exciting thing about that for me is when these signs are tagged or start to get weathered from the years and become incredibly unique even from 1 sign to another. This urban decay from the elements and human intervention produce some of the most beautiful things I can imagine. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
